DIAGNOSTICS
  E0200: stream query `one_order` uses `get` — a stream is many rows
  E0201: stream query `paged_orders` declares `page`
  E0202: mutation `place_order` cannot return a stream
  W0103: query `paged_orders` will scan `Order`: no index leads with any of (total)
SCHEMA
model Order  table=order
  id: Id
  status: text
  total: int
shape OrderCard from Order
query one_order  target=Order verb=get many stream  shape=OrderCard
query paged_orders  target=Order verb=list many stream  shape=OrderCard  page
mutation place_order  ret=Order
